.DT
query_finger_info
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_finger_info

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_finger_info -  This method returns all the info needed for a player's finger.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
class finger_info query_finger_info(string name)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the player to get the data for
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the player info for the player

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/player_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns all the info needed for a player's finger.
If the player is online, the updated values will be gotten
straight from the player object.
.EP

